* Urgent Email Broadcast
*   When to use:    In case of emergency (weather, course change, cancellation).
*   How to use:     Double-click to send an urgent email to all runners with an email address.
*   Setup:          Configure SendGrid API key and sender in Entries.INI (%email_apikey%, %email_from%).
Header

URGENT ALERT - %race name%

.End of Header
Destination         temp.txt
Records Per Page    1
Page Length         3
From Page Number    1
To Page Number      1000
No Column Headers
No Page Numbers
No Total

* Selection: All participants with an email address
Select              EMAIL
NE

* Message Construction
Message             URGENT: %race name% alert.
Line Feed
Message             Severe weather/thunderstorms approaching.
Line Feed
Message             Please seek shelter immediately and follow official instructions.

EMAIL TO            EMAIL
Email Subject       URGENT: %race name% Alert
EMAIL SERVER        sendgrid
EMAIL APIKEY        %email_apikey%
EMAIL FROM          %email_from%
